msgctxt "sn45.152:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.152:0.2"
msgid "12. Balakaraṇīyavagga"
msgstr "12. Hard Work"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.152:0.3"
msgid "152. Rukkhasutta"
msgstr "152. Trees"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.48"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.152:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho pācīnaninno pācīnapoṇo pācīnapabbhāro."
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose a tree slants, slopes, and inclines to the east."

#. VAR: mūlacchinno → mūle chinno (bj, pts1) | mūlacchinde kate (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn45.152:1.2"
msgid "So mūlacchinno katamena papateyyā”ti?"
msgstr "If it was cut off at the root, where would it fall?”"

msgctxt "sn45.152:1.3"
msgid "“Yena, bhante, ninno yena poṇo yena pabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, it would fall in the direction that it slants, slopes, and inclines.”"

msgctxt "sn45.152:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro."
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble "
"eightfold path slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment."

msgctxt "sn45.152:1.5"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant who develops the noble eightfold path slant, slope, "
"and incline to extinguishment?"

msgctxt "sn45.152:1.6"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti "
"vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ …"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.152:1.7"
msgid ""
"evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvento ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaronto nibbānaninno hoti nibbānapoṇo "
"nibbānapabbhāro”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant who develops and cultivates the noble eightfold path "
"slants, slopes, and inclines to extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.152:1.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
